paragraphs.title: What is the most used type of gas in France ?
paragraphs.text:
%hive 
select gas_label, count(gas_label) as count_gas from datacsv group by gas_label order by count_gas

paragraphs.title: Let first create a new table extracting the year and the department
paragraphs.text:
%hive
create table departments_year row format delimited fields terminated by '\073' AS select id_pos, gas_label, pop, price, SUBSTR(zip, 1,2) as departement, SUBSTR(daate, 1,4) as year from datacsv

paragraphs.title: Now let see if all department sells Gazole the most
paragraphs.text:
%hive
SELECT gas_label, count(gas_label) FROM(
    SELECT departement, max(named_struct('n',n,'gas_label', gas_label)).n, max(named_struct('n',n,'gas_label', gas_label)).gas_label FROM(
        SELECT departement, gas_label, count(*) as n
        FROM departments_year
        GROUP BY departement, gas_label)
        t
        GROUP BY departement order by gas_label ) u
        GROUP BY gas_label

paragraphs.title: Where is gazole the most expensive ?
paragraphs.text:
%hive 
select departement, gas_label, avg(price) as prix from departments_year where gas_label=='Gazole' group by departement, gas_label order by prix desc limit 5

paragraphs.title: In general what is the most expensive gas ?
paragraphs.text:
%hive
select gas_label, avg(price) as prix from datacsv group by gas_label order by prix desc
